captions.text:
"Improbable Square", all
players stand up, please.

Elidio and Andy
step ahead, please.

The two players at the front will start a
scene with a theme provided by you.

I ring the bell,
the square turns around.

The two players at the front will
start a scene with the same theme.
I ring the bell.

The players at the front will start
a third scene with the same theme,
the square turns.

The players at the front will start a
fourth scene with the same theme,
the square turns.

When the players in
the front are repeated,

they have to resume the scene
they were doing in the first round.

- I just need to hear your name.
- Daniela.

We need words starting
with a D that aren't 'dice'.

Dinosaur, who said that?
Thank you for your contribution.

'Dinosaur' is the theme for
"Improbable Square", starting now!

- Wouldn't it be easier to do with a broom?
- No, it must be delicate.

Every dust we take off
we discover a new...

You sure it isn't better
to use a vacuum cleaner...

- What is the name of that dinosaur, mom?
- Readosaurus, son.

- Readosaurus? Is he ready?
- He's always ready to strike!

- And the name of that one?
- That's the brutesaurus.

- Is he a brute?
- He's a brute!

- What about that one, mom?
- That's the streptosaurus.

- Is he strepting, mom?
- He's stressed out!
I want the green one...
Do you...
This isn't a dinosaur noise, is it?
This is a dino dog, it's cute.

No, my daughter likes dinosaurs
with dinosaur noise!
I have here...
No?
Super clean, right?
How long did you take to do this?
Oh boy, about ten minutes!
I got that thing that blows some air...

It's all out! There was some
skin ruining the bones!

- I threw it out...
- Ruined skin? Did it have skin?

- Yes it did, it was awful!
- Are you telling me...
Like decomposing, right?

And that one swinging the purse,
what's his name?

- It's whoresaurus!
- Whoresaurus?

- Whoresaurus!
- And what does the whoresaurus do?
He charges!

- Is this the asthmasaurus?
- We sell a lot of these...

And this wouldn't be possible
without mr. Raimundo's help,

who developed a new
technology for archaeology!
Just vacuum it!

Mom, what's the name of
the dinosaur that drives a car?

- It's prickosaurus!
- I thought I was the prick!
That's it! I'm taking this one!

If your party ever needs it,
hire Daniel Tauszig!
